meta_description: Jobcontax is a specialist Construction recruitment agency with operations in Ireland
paragraph:
JobContax is a specialist recruitment company in the Construction sector.
JobContax has recruited for construction companies in Ireland since 2001.
JobContax clients include Amec, Amgen, BHP Billiton, Carillion, Coca Cola, Emaar, GSK, Habtoor Leighton, Intel, Jacobs Engineering, J&J, Pfizer, Saint Gobain, Shell and many more.
